    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款像素风的经典塔防游戏，融合了肉鸽元素。你需要召唤亡魂来抵御敌人的进攻，每种亡魂都有独特的流派技能树，升级时会随机选择技能。游戏拥有无尽模式，你需要尽可能获得最高分来解锁更多的技能树。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以建造自己独特的迷宫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/193152fababbe7cbbe29a831ba61bde7.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8种独特的防御塔，拥有各自独特的职业技能：偷盗、减速、眩晕、暴击、多重箭、嗜血、毒箭、减甲...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/2fd5b3850e0c9228f556f887503e467f.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >杀怪可以提升经验等级，经验等级升级后可以随机选择独特的职业技能，构筑自己的流派。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/99d9efd53d0a64926d1534113a11fbf5.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你可以调整关卡难度来获得更高的得分。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/6c179da086929616dc6c846dacd3a05e.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >升级你的技能树获得永久提升！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.poster.avif?t=1744450793\" width=568 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.webm?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/b0b2073f19dfe64a714b6355fa5c1fad.mp4?t=1744450793\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >成就系统，解锁更多的魂器，挑战更高的难度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras/3cb8713c9930d03235ccaf1f20c2dc71.avif?t=1744450793\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3082690/extras_big/3cb8713c9930d03235ccaf1f20c2dc71.avif?t=1744450793 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >感兴趣就加入愿望单吧！这样我会更有动力更新更多内容！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><a href=\"mailto:如果你有更好的想法，请发邮件联系我！我的邮箱：hangyi824@foxmail.com\">如果你有更好的想法，请发邮件联系我！我的邮箱：hangyi824@foxmail.com</a></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >欢迎加入qq群：857285717</p>",
